Class CSVFile.CSVFileBuilder

java.lang.Object
src.ai.data.csv.CSVFile.CSVFileBuilder
Enclosing class:
CSVFile
private static class CSVFile.CSVFileBuilder extends Object
A class to build a CSVFileReader by setting the specific information about the CSV file that is being read.
